UNITED STATES ex rel. Gene McCANN, Appellant, v. Tom C. CLARK, Attorney General, James E. Mulcahy, United States Marshal, and E. E. Thompson, Warden, Appellees. No. 111, Docket 20388. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 26, 1946. Gene McCann, pro se. John J. Donovan, Jr., of New York City, for appellees.

Before L. HAND, CHASE, and FRANK, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
